# Phase Completion Reports

Every phase deliverable must include sections **A–J**:

| Section | Content |
|---------|---------|
| A | Completion Report |
| B | Architecture Compliance |
| C | Database Changes |
| D | APIs |
| E | Vue Components |
| F | Security Impact |
| G | Performance Impact |
| H | Responsive Design Notes |
| I | Testing Strategy |
| J | Deployment Notes |

Also document seed data changes when applicable (see seed-data rule).
